### Enrichment
Industry trend: regex-only PII detection has high false positives. RECAP framework combines regex with context-aware LLMs for better accuracy. DataFog (Python SDK) combines regex + NLP pipelines. PiiCatcher uses regex + spaCy NER. Consider augmenting the 40+ regex patterns with a lightweight NLP layer for context-aware detection to reduce false positives while maintaining the deterministic first pass.

